Stop applying growth serum when the value is high to avoid risking a negative outcome. The 'mutation catalyst' consistently decreased value in my rounds, so avoid using it. Do not combine items that already have negative values or many features, as this tends to result in very low scores. The hint 'combine up to three' refers to the *number of components* within a single item, not the number of items you can select in one 'action' (which is always two). Your score is the value of your most valuable item, but cannot drop below zero.
